    • Constructor Detail

      • BTOProject

        public BTOProject​(int projectId,
                  String name,
                  String neighbourhood,
                  List<FlatType> flatType,
                  HashMap<FlatType,​Integer> flatCount,
                  HashMap<FlatType,​Integer> flatPrice,
                  Date applicationOpeningDate,
                  Date applicationClosingDate,
                  HDBManager projectManager,
                  List<String> assignedOfficers,
                  int availableOfficerSlots,
                  boolean visibility)
        Constructor to initialise the BTOProject object with common attributes.
        Parameters:
        projectId - The unique identifier for the BTO project.
        name - The name of the BTO project.
        neighbourhood - The neighbourhood where the BTO project is located.
        flatType - A List containing the type of flats available in the BTO project (e.g., "2 Room Flat", "3 Room Flat").
        flatCount - A HashMap containing the count of each flat type available/remaining in the project.
        flatPrice - A HashMap containing the price of each flat type available in the project.
        applicationOpeningDate - The date when applications for the BTO project open.
        applicationClosingDate - The date when applications for the BTO project close.
        projectManager - The HDBManager responsible for managing the BTO project.
        assignedOfficers - A list of HDBOfficers assigned to assist with the BTO project.
        availableOfficerSlots - The number of available slots for HDBOfficers to be assigned to the project.
        visibility - Indicates whether the project is visible to users or not.

      • BTOProject

        public BTOProject​(int projectId,
                  String name,
                  String neighbourhood,
                  List<FlatType> flatType,
                  HashMap<FlatType,​Integer> flatCount,
                  HashMap<FlatType,​Integer> flatCountRemaining,
                  HashMap<FlatType,​Integer> flatPrice,
                  Date applicationOpeningDate,
                  Date applicationClosingDate,
                  HDBManager projectManager,
                  List<String> assignedOfficers,
                  int availableOfficerSlots,
                  boolean visibility)
        Constructor for importing BTOProject objects from CSV file. Should ONLY be called from BTOProjectDB.readFromCSV().
        Parameters:
        projectId - The unique identifier for the BTO project.
        name - The name of the BTO project.
        neighbourhood - The neighbourhood where the BTO project is located.
        flatType - A List containing the type of flats available in the BTO project (e.g., "2 Room Flat", "3 Room Flat").
        flatCount - A HashMap containing the count of each flat type available in the project.
        flatCountRemaining - A HashMap containing the count of each flat type remaining in the project.
        flatPrice - A HashMap containing the price of each flat type available in the project.
        applicationOpeningDate - The date when applications for the BTO project open.
        applicationClosingDate - The date when applications for the BTO project close.
        projectManager - The HDBManager responsible for managing the BTO project.
        assignedOfficers - A list of HDBOfficers assigned to assist with the BTO project.
        availableOfficerSlots - The number of available slots for HDBOfficers to be assigned to the project.
        visibility - Indicates whether the project is visible to users or not.
